item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Utility_Network_Firewall_Rule_Attribute
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Utility_Network_Firewall_Rule_Attribute Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Utility_Network_Firewall_Rule_Attribute data type contains information relating to a single firewall rule. Local actions The valid actions for use with rules. Type: array of strings maximumRuleCount Maximum allowed number of rules. Type: integer protocols The valid protocols for use with rules. Type: array of strings sourceIpSubnetMasks The valid source ip subnet masks for use with rules.
